  <Box HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="10" Orientation="Vertical" VerticalAlignment="Stretch">

    Welcome to [color=#ffd781]Vermist Dust Sector[/color], a server focused on improvisational storytelling. If you're here, you probably already know that. [bold]You must be 20+ to play here.[/bold]

    Feel free to AHelp if you need any gameplay or rule clarifications. When in doubt, if it's fun for everyone involved, it's probably alright. Unsure if it would be fun for the others? LOOC in-game or OOC in the lobby and ask!

    [bold]Please read the rules.[/bold] Don't worry, we're quite lenient and operate mostly on self-moderating community respect and good faith. Beyond [color=#ffd781][bold]Section I: Community Rules[/bold][/color], the rest can be considered guidelines rather than strict law. This does not mean we will tolerate behaviour that clashes with the server's ideals.

    <Box HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="5" Orientation="Vertical" VerticalAlignment="Stretch">
      [color=#449944][bold]Engaging with the community in good faith is what allows Vermist to be Vermist![/bold][/color]
